Mixing.Description: In a typical synthesis of BT@PHEMA@PMMA NPs, 0.5 g of initiator grafted BT NPs, 5 mL HEMA, and 5 mL DI water were combined in a round-bottom flask and sonicated for 30 min.

Additive.Description: 0.5 mmol CuBr (0.0715 g) and 0.1 mmol CuBr2 (0.0225 g) were added to the flask.

Mixing.Description: 1.2 mmol bpy (0.187 g) was dissolved in 1 mL degassed ethanol and the solution was added to the flask via a syringe.
